## Summary of Improvements

Based on research from [dev.to](https://dev.to/metro_wantsummore_f2fa24c/built-a-simple-box-breathing-pwa-to-help-you-relax-1kf), [apps.apple.com](https://apps.apple.com/us/app/box-breathing-float/id1605558336), and [headspace.com](https://www.headspace.com/content/mindful-activity/box-breathing/5647):

| Feature | Improvement |
|---------|-------------|
| **Haptic Feedback** | Added vibration on phase transitions (Vibration API) |
| **Multiple Patterns** | Box, 4-7-8 Relaxing, Energizing, Calming |
| **Audio** | Different Solfeggio-inspired frequencies per phase |
| **Stats Tracking** | Sessions, minutes, cycles, and streak tracking via localStorage |
| **Starting Countdown** | 3-2-1 countdown before session starts |
| **Pause/Resume** | True pause that preserves progress |
| **Session Summary** | Shows duration and cycles on completion |
| **Pace Control** | Slider to adjust timing (faster/slower) |
| **Better PWA** | Enhanced manifest with shortcuts, screenshots, icons |
| **Accessibility** | ARIA labels, roles, live regions |
| **Safe Areas** | Proper iOS notch/home indicator handling |
| **Visual Polish** | Smoother animations, better typography, corner indicators |
| **Wake Lock Reacquisition** | Re-acquires on visibility change |
| **Stale-While-Revalidate** | Better caching strategy in service worker |